can stand up.

01:19:02.620 --> 01:19:45.740
At the very outset you have to now understand
that we are going to enter into the Kingdom

01:19:45.740 --> 01:19:56.389
of God and hence we have to little bit unload
ourselves.

01:19:56.389 --> 01:20:09.650
One of the conditions is that we should not
feel guilty – one should not feel guilty

01:20:09.650 --> 01:20:10.650
at all.

01:20:10.650 --> 01:20:14.200
Yesterday, same problem I said, but you were
still feeling guilty.

01:20:14.200 --> 01:20:15.750
Also it’s a fashion.

01:20:15.750 --> 01:20:20.200
Also I think the language is such – all
the time sorry, sorry, sorry, sorry…

01:20:20.200 --> 01:20:25.040
Even when we used to receive telephones we
used to say “I beg your pardon.”

01:20:25.040 --> 01:20:27.700
But now it is sorry, sorry, sorry – ten
times sorry.

01:20:27.700 --> 01:20:33.000
What is there to be so sorry?

01:20:33.000 --> 01:20:35.920
So we have to be pleasantly placed towards
ourselves.

01:20:35.920 --> 01:20:37.710
We have to respect ourselves.

01:20:37.710 --> 01:20:40.790
We have to be happy about ourselves.

01:20:40.790 --> 01:20:48.520
This is first thing is not to feel guilty
about anything - just believe that you have

01:20:48.520 --> 01:20:55.650
done nothing wrong which cannot be dissolved
by this great power of forgiveness.

01:20:55.650 --> 01:20:59.240
Please believe Me.

01:20:59.240 --> 01:21:05.440
But if you want to stick onto a feeling like
that – “No, no, I am guilty” – it’s

01:21:05.440 --> 01:21:06.590
only mental.

01:21:06.590 --> 01:21:14.090
Animals don’t feel guilty about anything
– a dog will bark, tiger will eat anything

01:21:14.090 --> 01:21:15.710
that it wants to.

01:21:15.710 --> 01:21:20.090
It’s only human beings who feel that way
– that I’ve done this wrong, I’ve done

01:21:20.090 --> 01:21:21.090
that wrong.

01:21:21.090 --> 01:21:26.400
All right, so not to feel guilty that’s
one point.

01:21:26.400 --> 01:21:37.920
The second one is to forgive everyone, which
is very difficult for many people.

01:21:37.920 --> 01:21:45.170
I don’t know how many mounds of unhappiness
is in the head because we cannot forgive.

01:21:45.170 --> 01:21:50.280
Mounds, it’s not kilos and kilos.

01:21:50.280 --> 01:21:59.050
Yesterday I found most of them had not forgiven
and I had to go on putting balm on their heads

01:21:59.050 --> 01:22:00.770
to take out.

01:22:00.770 --> 01:22:03.460
So you must cooperate.

01:22:03.460 --> 01:22:08.040
Just forgive, just forgive everyone.

01:22:08.040 --> 01:22:12.050
First of all forgive yourself and forgive
everyone.

01:22:12.050 --> 01:22:17.570
And be pleasantly placed towards yourself.

01:22:17.570 --> 01:22:20.710
There’s no Greek tragedy going on here – no
tragedy.

01:22:20.710 --> 01:22:31.410
We are in a very beautiful atmosphere and
we are going to go into the most beautiful

01:22:31.410 --> 01:22:35.300
area within ourselves, that is our spirit.

01:22:35.300 --> 01:22:40.520
So we have to be very light about it.

01:22:40.520 --> 01:22:49.830
All right, with all this understanding, I
have to request you that we have to take out

01:22:49.830 --> 01:22:57.199
your shoes because this Mother Earth also
helps us a lot.

01:22:57.199 --> 01:23:17.910
And not to be serious – not to be serious
about it.

01:23:17.910 --> 01:23:31.730
It’s not frivolous, but it’s fun.

01:23:31.730 --> 01:23:50.000
So you have to put your left hand towards
Me, which represents your desire to get realization.

01:23:50.000 --> 01:23:56.690
If all the Sahaja Yogis could also sit down
it would be very nice.

01:23:56.690 --> 01:23:59.980
Please be seated and don’t move about.

01:23:59.980 --> 01:24:06.250
Left hand towards Me like that – be comfortable,
if you want you can put it on your lap or

01:24:06.250 --> 01:24:08.230
you can put it up if you want to.

01:24:08.230 --> 01:24:21.210
Then the right hand needs to be used for nourishing
your centers on the left-hand side.

01:24:21.210 --> 01:24:25.530
Now I’ll show you how we’ll be nourishing.

01:24:25.530 --> 01:24:30.090
Before that, please remember that put your
both the feet apart from each other – not

01:24:30.090 --> 01:24:33.960
too much, but slightly.

01:24:33.960 --> 01:24:40.080
Now, left hand towards Me.

01:24:40.080 --> 01:24:47.350
I’ll show you before and then we can close
our eyes and work it out.

01:24:47.350 --> 01:25:00.190
Put your right hand on your heart – in the
heart resides the Spirit and Kundalini is

01:25:00.190 --> 01:25:08.420
the reflection of the Holy Ghost, of the Adi
Shakti, within us, while the Spirit is the

01:25:08.420 --> 01:25:13.449
reflection of God Almighty.

01:25:13.449 --> 01:25:21.270
So we put our attention to our heart first.

01:25:21.270 --> 01:25:29.250
Then we take our right hand in the upper portion
of our abdomen on the left-hand side and press

01:25:29.250 --> 01:25:30.560
it hard.

01:25:30.560 --> 01:25:34.920
This is the center of our mastery.

01:25:34.920 --> 01:25:43.960
We take down our right hand on the lower portion
of our abdomen and press it hard.

01:25:43.960 --> 01:25:55.480
This is the center of pure knowledge that
manifests on our central nervous system.

01:25:55.480 --> 01:26:05.150
We take back our hand in the upper portion
of our abdomen.

01:26:05.150 --> 01:26:14.050
And again we take it in the heart, in the
upper portion of our heart.

01:26:14.050 --> 01:26:23.081
Then we take it in the corner of our neck
and our shoulder and put your head to the

01:26:23.081 --> 01:26:25.760
right.

01:26:25.760 --> 01:26:34.820
This is the center we catch when we feel guilty.

01:26:34.820 --> 01:26:49.480
Then we take our hand on our forehead and
slowly bring down our head on it to rest.

01:26:49.480 --> 01:27:00.590
Here we press it on both the sides and this
is the center to forgive.

01:27:00.590 --> 01:27:14.400
We take back our hand on the back side of
our head and put our head resting on it - this

01:27:14.400 --> 01:27:20.250
is the center for asking forgiveness without
feeling guilty.

01:27:20.250 --> 01:27:30.520
We stretch our hand, with the center of our
palm, we put it on our head in the soft bone

01:27:30.520 --> 01:27:39.290
area of our childhood, called as fontanelle
bone area, and slowly we put down our head.

01:27:39.290 --> 01:27:54.420
Here we stretch our fingers and move our scalp
carefully with pressure, slowly, clockwise,

01:27:54.420 --> 01:28:00.380
seven times.

01:28:00.380 --> 01:28:18.920
That’s all we have to do.

01:28:18.920 --> 01:28:27.560
Now please close your eyes and don’t open
them until I ask you to open because attention

01:28:27.560 --> 01:28:29.320
has to go inside.

01:28:29.320 --> 01:28:32.050
Put your left hand towards Me.

01:28:32.050 --> 01:28:37.260
Now first you will feel thoughtless – so
don’t fight with your thoughts.

01:28:37.260 --> 01:28:39.440
Automatically everything will work out.

01:28:39.440 --> 01:28:47.670
Don’t fight with your thoughts, just keep
watching and ultimately you will feel cool

01:28:47.670 --> 01:28:52.680
breeze coming out of your fontanelle bone
area and you’ll also start feeling cool

01:28:52.680 --> 01:28:59.200
breeze all around you which is the cool breeze
of the Holy Ghost, the cool breeze of the

01:28:59.200 --> 01:29:09.400
all-pervading power as described by Adi Shankaracharya,
Salilam, salilam – it’s cool, and cool.

01:29:09.400 --> 01:29:22.420
So now, we put our left hand this way towards
Me and the right hand on the heart.

01:29:22.420 --> 01:29:31.800
Here you have to ask Me a very fundamental
question, three times – “Mother, am I

01:29:31.800 --> 01:29:33.500
the Spirit?”

01:29:33.500 --> 01:29:42.500
In your heart, ask the question “Mother,
am I the Spirit?”

01:29:42.500 --> 01:29:54.120
If you are the spirit you are your master,
because in the light of your spirit you know

01:29:54.120 --> 01:29:58.730
what is right and what is wrong – you can
guide yourself.

01:29:58.730 --> 01:30:05.510
So put your right hand in the upper portion
of your abdomen on the left-hand side, and

01:30:05.510 --> 01:30:16.300
here please ask Me a question again three
times – “Mother, am I my own master?”

01:30:16.300 --> 01:30:25.800
“Mother, am I my own master?”

01:30:25.800 --> 01:30:36.760
As I have told you that I will not cross your
freedom, I respect your freedom, and only

01:30:36.760 --> 01:30:46.640
if you want I can bestow this pure knowledge
on yourself, otherwise I cannot.

01:30:46.640 --> 01:30:54.560
So please put your right hand in the lower
portion of your abdomen and ask the question,

01:30:54.560 --> 01:31:09.290
“Mother” - or you can request “Mother
please give me pure knowledge.”

01:31:09.290 --> 01:31:17.560
Say this six times because this center has
got six petals.

01:31:17.560 --> 01:31:29.830
“Mother, please give me pure knowledge.”

01:31:29.830 --> 01:31:42.110
Now all the prophets of the past and the saints
and seers have built up for us a center of

01:31:42.110 --> 01:31:44.300
mastery.

01:31:44.300 --> 01:31:54.840
But to open the center we have to have all
the confidence, so please raise your hand

01:31:54.840 --> 01:32:06.469
and put it in the upper portion of your abdomen
on the left-hand side and say with full confidence

01:32:06.469 --> 01:32:19.810
to nourish this center, ten times, “Mother,
I am my own master.”

01:32:19.810 --> 01:32:32.680
Please say this ten times.

01:32:32.680 --> 01:32:46.090
Now we have to know that we are not this body,
we are not this mind, we are not these emotions,

01:32:46.090 --> 01:32:50.900
we are not this intellect.

01:32:50.900 --> 01:32:55.710
We are not our conditionings or are we our
ego.

01:32:55.710 --> 01:33:00.160
We are pure spirit.

01:33:00.160 --> 01:33:09.760
So now raise your hand to your heart and with
full confidence say twelve times “Mother,

01:33:09.760 --> 01:33:11.830
I am the spirit.”

01:33:11.830 --> 01:33:21.710
Please say twelve times, “Mother, I am the
spirit.”

01:33:21.710 --> 01:33:35.550
You have to know that this Divine Power is
the ocean of love and compassion.

01:33:35.550 --> 01:33:46.390
It is the ocean of joy and bliss but above
all it is the ocean of forgiveness, so there

01:33:46.390 --> 01:33:55.469
is no mistake that you have committed which
cannot be dissolved by this ocean.

01:33:55.469 --> 01:34:05.640
So please forgive yourself and put your right
hand in the corner of your neck and your shoulder

01:34:05.640 --> 01:34:09.840
and turn your head to your right.

01:34:09.840 --> 01:34:24.540
Here you have to say with complete confidence
again, “Shri Mataji, I am not guilty at

01:34:24.540 --> 01:34:25.540
all.”

01:34:25.540 --> 01:34:44.120
Or you can call Me Mother – “Mother, I
am not guilty at all.”

01:34:44.120 --> 01:34:59.560
Sixteen times- please say this sixteen times.

01:34:59.560 --> 01:35:12.800
Now one has to know whether you forgive someone
or don’t forgive, you don’t do anything

01:35:12.800 --> 01:35:14.980
– it’s a myth.

01:35:14.980 --> 01:35:19.730
But if you don’t forgive, then you play
into wrong hands.

01:35:19.730 --> 01:35:31.490
So put your right hand on your forehead and
please bend your head, resting on the hand

01:35:31.490 --> 01:35:37.660
as much as you can and now press it on both
the sides.

01:35:37.660 --> 01:35:46.380
And here please, please, say it from your
heart “Mother, I forgive everyone.”

01:35:46.380 --> 01:35:55.239
Please say it from your heart - please say
it, otherwise again I will have to work very

01:35:55.239 --> 01:35:56.280
hard on you.

01:35:56.280 --> 01:36:01.380
So please say it from your heart – “Mother,
I forgive everyone.”

01:36:01.380 --> 01:36:08.670
You are not going to miss your self-realization
for not forgiving, please.

01:36:08.670 --> 01:36:24.380
How many lives you have been seeking the truth
that this time you are not going to miss it

01:36:24.380 --> 01:36:25.380
out.

01:36:25.380 --> 01:37:18.820
Now take back your hand on the back side of
your head and push back 

01:37:18.820 --> 01:39:24.980
your head as much as you can resting on 
your 

01:39:24.980 --> 01:39:55.390
hand 

01:39:55.390 --> 01:40:19.070
and here for your own satisfaction, without
feeling guilty, without counting your mistakes,

01:40:19.070 --> 01:40:37.750
please say, “Oh Divine, if 

01:40:37.750 --> 01:41:10.160
I 

01:41:10.160 --> 01:41:35.239
